# Project structure

When adding or moving code in this repo, follow **PROJECT_SCHEMA.md** at the project root.

- **New page/screen** → `src/pages/<Name>.jsx` + register route.
- **New reusable UI** → `src/components/ui/` (primitives) or the right feature folder under `src/components/`.
- **New API call/entity** → `src/api/` (extend or add file).
- **New server route** → `server/src/<domain>/` (e.g. auth, admin, payments); keep handlers thin, logic in `server/src/logic/`.
- **New business rule** → `server/src/logic/`.
- **Naming**: React components/pages PascalCase; hooks `use*`; utils and server modules camelCase; directories and config files lowercase-with-dashes.
